<Class name="CMIF_InterfaceMsgController" id="37f54c4e-8048-4e12-92d7-caeadca0cc11">
    <superclass name="CMIF_InterfaceObject"/>
    <transient/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>Used by the CM_TCPInterfaceAgent.

One instance will be created for each incoming message, and the response lines will be created as
children of this object, before the response string is created.

NOTE - IMPORTANT:
*****************
If you add or rename any property on this class please check the
PortSchema::CM_InterfaceHistory::doTranslations method has the correct name.
</text>
